metadata.title: Elevation (1:250,000 Scale Generalized)
metadata.description: Data Type: Elevation;  This layer contains merged and generalized elevation data based on 1:250,000 scale DEM's for Prince William Sound - Copper River ecosystem. The data have been generalized from the full resolution DEM's organized by 250,000 scale quadrangle boundaries. Related data sets include the 1:63,360 scale DEM's and shaded relief images. This layer contains merged and generalized elevation data based on 1:250,000 scale DEM's for Prince William Sound - Copper River ecosystem. The data have been generalized from the full resolution DEM's organized by 250,000 scale quadrangle boundaries. Related data sets include the 1:63,360 scale DEM's and shaded relief mages.
